latestPosts.caption:
Presenting to you ‘JURASSIC-Not Directed by Spielberg’
Graduation Design Collection 2022
It is an ‘Avant Garde’ Knitwear Collection inspired by Dinosaurs. 
It takes us on a journey to the Jurassic world where we get a glimpse of the gigantic creatures craft-fully depicted through each ensemble.
Each ensemble depicts a category of Dinosaur. 
All the textures are presented through various knitting and crocheting techniques that all together give a different dimension to the entire concept.
My goal was to show an ‘out of the box’ approach to Knitwear Design in the Avant Garde genre.
Sandra Buckland’a work motivated me to think in these lines and explore the unlimited possibilities of knitting. 

A Big Thank you to @newagestudios57 @bhaskar_romit @jitanshu_s @iftiaz_akib @beautybymeghalika @rohini_aich_rohh @shrija_d @sohamsil_ @the_inconsolable_rebel @kushol_kk for all your help, support and immense contribution throughout❤️
This entire project would not have been possible without you people. I am blessed to have you guys in my life. Keep supporting me and motivating me just like this in all my future endeavours.

“Inspired by the bold elegance of #MetGala2025, I’ve conceptualised a look that speaks of timeless grandeur and modern strength. This ensemble blends classic Spanish silhouettes with opulent tailoring, embroidered in rich gold on deep emerald and black hues. The dramatic trail, detailed cuff work, and structured jacket tell a story of power, poise, and regal artistry. A tribute to fine craftsmanship and the spirit of couture.”
- Designed by Titir Sengupta
